00:01:30.435 --> 00:01:33.275
Jellyfish gave rise
to the first chordates.

00:01:33.299 --> 00:01:36.967
The first chordates gave rise
to the first vertebrates.

00:01:37.277 --> 00:01:39.695
The vertebrates came out of the sea,

00:01:39.719 --> 00:01:41.055
and here we are.

00:01:42.737 --> 00:01:48.327
